Why this license
----------------

ChessPrint embeds the "caliente" chess piece set (by avi,
https://github.com/avi-0/caliente, obtained via lichess-org/lila), which is
itself licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. The ShareAlike clause requires that any
distribution combining or adapting that material be released under the same
license, so the project as a whole adopts CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. See the NOTICE file
for third-party attribution details.


